dent 17 year old, Noah resists living in a mansion surrounded by luxury. However, it is there where she meets Nick, her new stepbrother, and the clash of their strong personalities becomes evident from the very beginning.","genre_ids":[18,10749,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":28.0117,"vote_count":4003,"poster_path":"/w46Vw536HwNnEzOa7J24YH9DPRS.jpg","release_date":"2023-06-08","vote_average":7.758,"backdrop_path":"/oz4U9eA6ilYf1tyiVuGmkftdLac.jpg","original_title":"Culpa mía","original_language":"es"},{"id":762975,"adult":false,"title":"Purple Hearts","video":false,"overview":"An aspiring musician agrees to a marriage of convenience with a soon-to-deploy Marine, but a tragedy soon turns their fake relationship all too real.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.3448,"vote_count":2832,"poster_path":"/4JyNWkryifWbWXJyxcWh3pVya6N.jpg","release_date":"2022-07-29","vote_average":8.048,"backdrop_path":"/jdZM1Gs6DtRGvosgqaXRrIkvYX7.jpg","original_title":"Purple Hearts","original_language":"en"},{"id":744275,"adult":false,"title":"After We Fell","video":false,"overview":"Just as Tessa's life begins to become unglued, nothing is what she thought it would be. Not her friends nor her family. The only person that she should be able to rely on is Hardin, who is furious when he discovers the massive secret that she's been keeping. Before Tessa makes the biggest decision of her life, everything changes because of revelations about her family.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.6211,"vote_count":2701,"poster_path":"/dU4HfnTEJDf9KvxGS9hgO7BVeju.jpg","release_date":"2021-09-01","vote_average":7.013,"backdrop_path":"/mxdiaM2tsx8M6W3zLgiPwAkhQfq.jpg","original_title":"After We Fell","original_language":"en"},{"id":774825,"adult":false,"title":"The Ice Age Adventures of Buck Wild","video":false,"overview":"The fearless one-eyed weasel Buck teams up with mischievous possum brothers Crash & Eddie as they head off on a new adventure into